---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy: JetAvenue" description="JetAvenue privacy policy. How we collect, use, and protect your information.">
  <div class="legal-page">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>When you contact us through our website or by phone, we may collect your name, email address, phone number, and details about your aircraft and service needs. We do not collect payment information through this website.</p>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use the information you provide solely to respond to your service inquiries, schedule assessments, and communicate with you about our maintenance services. We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>

    <h2>Communications</h2>
    <p>By submitting a contact form or calling us, you consent to being contacted by JetAvenue regarding your inquiry. You may opt out of non-essential communications at any time by contacting us at <a href="mailto:mx@jetavenue.net">mx@jetavenue.net</a>.</p>

    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    <p>We take reasonable precautions to protect your information. However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure. We cannot guarantee absolute security of your data.</p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>Our website may use third-party analytics tools (such as Google Analytics) to help us understand site usage. These services may collect anonymized usage data subject to their own privacy policies.</p>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>Our site may use cookies for basic functionality and analytics. You can disable cookies in your browser settings, though some features may not function as intended.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal information at any time by contacting us at <a href="mailto:mx@jetavenue.net">mx@jetavenue.net</a>.</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For privacy-related questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:mx@jetavenue.net">mx@jetavenue.net</a> or call <a href="tel:8004805387">800-480-JETS</a>.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-md);
  }
  .legal-page h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 42px);
    font-weight: 800; color: var(--color-ink); margin: 0 0 8px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .last-updated {
    font-size: 13px; color: var(--color-body); margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg);
  }
  .legal-page h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-ink); margin: var(--space-lg) 0 8px;
  }
  .legal-page p {
    font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 15px; color: var(--color-body);
    line-height: 1.7; margin: 0;
  }
  .legal-page a { color: var(--color-brand); text-decoration: none; }
  .legal-page a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
</style>
